    "section_testimonials_nqbFCX": {
      "type": "section-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "text_BjRnU6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Well thought out placement of our basketball hoop which had driveway challenges. Perfect installation and great communication. High quality hoop. Highly recommend for install.</p>",
            "name": "Brian Bortman",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_YXjaNA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>We are 2nd generation clients of Fenceworks. And this 2nd round did not disappoint. Jake from Fenceworks helped us install an in ground basketball hoop. Our kids are 5 and 8. We were initially 50-50 on if we wanted to finally do this. And make the investment. We are glad we did. On day 1 of it being installed, it was a rainy gloomy evening. And instead of our kids asking to play video games or watch TV, they asked \"can we go out in the rain and play basketball?!\" Instantly we knew this was the right choice. As an amenity for the house. As a benefit to get our kids more active. To bring years of memories and activities. I have already referred Jake and Fencework to friends and my real estate clients for basketball hoops and fences, as we were pleased working with this family company.</p>",
            "name": "Joel Holland",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_HKmkXW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Jake and the team did an outstanding job installing our driveway basketball hoop. Top quality product, and seamless ordering and installation. The kids love it - thanks!</p>",
            "name": "Robert McQueen",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_dX9tyP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Jake, the basketball hoop looks great. Bob did a wonderful job with the installation and our grandsons love it. Almost wish we had a need for a fence so we could use you again.<br/>We would recommend you to anyone.</p>",
            "name": "Steve Kramer",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_GGm7hJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Great experience from start to finish- Jake was a pleasure to work with- great quality basketball hoop that was professionally installed in a timely fashion at competitive price. Highly recommend!</p>",
            "name": "Herschel Rush",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_VycMrV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>As good of an experience as anything I’ve purchased recently. From the treatment & education Jake gave me in the showroom, to the customer service through installation of my new basketball hoop, to my kids reaction seeing it for the first time. There is no place that checks all the boxes like Fenceworks.</p>",
            "name": "Marc Silverman",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_JhdKaG": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>A+++ experience.<br/><br/>Sean G was fast to respond and helped explain every single detail. The basketball hoop quality is great and they installed it ASAP<br/><br/>Would highly recommend to everybody</p>",
            "name": "Ricky Silverman",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        }
      },
